Annotations.Name: Water channel
Annotations.Description: Water channel annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress at the base of the B–C loop near the C-terminus of the B helix.

Annotations.Name: Channel 2b
Annotations.Description: Channel 2b annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress between the B–B′ loop and the β1 and β3 sheets.

Annotations.Name: Solvent channel
Annotations.Description: Solvent channel annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress between E, F, and I helices and the β5 sheet.

Annotations.Name: Channel 2c
Annotations.Description: Channel 2c annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress between the G and I helices and the B′ helix/B–C loop.

Annotations.Name: Channel 2e
Annotations.Description: Channel 2e annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress through the B–C loop.

Annotations.Name: Channel 2f
Annotations.Description: Channel 2f annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress between the F′ helix/F–G loop, and the β5 sheet.

Annotations.Name: Channel 3
Annotations.Description: Channel 3 annotated according to Cojocaru et al has egress between the F and G helices or at the E–F loop.
